hey may have violated both regulations above.<br />\n<br />\nBelow are some evidence of the official announcement from HKPF.https://<a href=\"http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/hong-kong-law-and-crime/article/2152375/hong-kong-police-launch-new-online-reporting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fhong-kong-law-and-crime%2Farticle%2F2152375%2Fhong-kong-police-launch-new-online-reporting&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReq6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=f5ee967d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/hong-kong-law-and-crime/article/2152375/hong-kong-police-launch-new-online-reporting</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0_yqH3GAnL8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0_yqH3GAnL8&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReq6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=157fdb47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0_yqH3GAnL8</a><br />\n<br />\nThese are the numbers HKPF used for the hotlines:5566 95005566 95015566 95025566 95035566 95045566 95055566 95065566 95075566 95085566 9509<br />\n<br />\nI know that Whatsapp has been enforcing on abusers of the platform. (<a href=\"https://tcrn.ch/31sotDa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftcrn.ch%2F31sotDa&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReq6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=452ad38f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tcrn.ch/31sotDa</a>)And I hope your company could look into the matters seriously to rule out anyone abusing the platform.I look forward to hearing from you soon.<br />\nYours faithfully,A loyal user in Hong Kong"}]}